abstract: >-
  Ontology2Graph generates synthetic knowledge graphs using
  generative AI and graph fusion, taking an RDFS/OWL
  ontology as input. Typical applications include testing
  the robustness of AI pipelines, benchmarking databases,
  and ensuring the replicability of experiments without
  sharing sensitive data.
